Description
-----------

This CVar changes the filtering on shadow buffers.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_sb_linearfilter [Boolean]

Parameters
----------

-   [Boolean]
    -   0 - Use GL\_NEAREST.
    -   1 - Use GL\_LINEAR.

